OL,5, Stroke patients should be offered extra
OL,6, rehabilitation on the NHS, say updated 
OL,7, guidelines for England and Wales.      
OL,9,FThe National Institute for Health and  
OL,10,FCare Excellence (NICE) had previously  
OL,11,Frecommended 45 minutes a day.          
OL,13,FBut it believes some patients may need 
OL,14,Fmore intensive therapy for recovery and
OL,15,Fis suggesting three hours a day, five  
OL,16,Fdays a week.                           
OL,18,FExperts welcome the advice, but        
OL,19,Fquestion how feasible it will be for a 
OL,20,Fstretched health service to deliver.   
